                            <comment id="476687" author="bzzz" created="Thu, 30 Oct 2025 09:28:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I noticed EFAULT in __ll_dio_user_copy() after failed ll_iov_iter_fault_in_readable() and that resulted in failing writes - very rary but still.&lt;br/&gt;
with the patch applied I can&apos;t reproduce this any more (will keep trying though).&lt;br/&gt;
not really sure about exact root cause but it looks like the spinlock somehow prevented page allocation or something in that area - I used get_user_pages_remote() to check pgtable content, but it was returning no pages after a failed ll_iov_iter_fault_in_readable()&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
